snippet.title: MechWarrior 5: Clans Teaser
snippet.description:
MECHWARRIOR 5: CLANS follows a Star of Clan Smoke Jaguar warriors during Operation REVIVAL, a full-scale invasion of the Inner Sphere. Armed with an arsenal of cutting-edge BattleMechs, meticulously designed maps and missions deliver immersive and intricate tactical gameplay and combat experiences.

MechWarrior 5 Clans is Available Now! 
https://mw5clans.com/purchase

- Experience challenging and immersive missions on multiple worlds.
- Pilot your Omnimech with streamlined Mech controls
- Command your Star with the intuitive Command Wheel, and dynamic Battlegrid.
- All new CLAN-themed metagame, Mechlab, and Pilot Progression.
- Playable with 1 to 5 Players with Cross-play Co-op on PlayStation 5, Xbox Series S|X, and PC 

Visit https://mw5clans.com/
